# Phase Kickoff Assessment

At phase start:

1. Align phase definition in `docs/maintainers/ROADMAP.md`, `docs/maintainers/TASKS.md`, and status YAML.
2. Confirm ready queue supports phase goals.
3. Define evidence expectations for phase-exit confidence.
4. Identify human-only decisions early.

